title: David Gates - slices of Bread
description:
David Gates - former front man in Bread - released a number of album during 1973 - 1981. These albums has not been remastered and reissued on CD.

Here are the best and the most from:

First - 1973
Second - 1975
Goodbye girl - 1978
Falling in love again - 1980
Take me now - 1981

These are vinyl rips, processed to eliminate noise, and packed as 2 albums.

Enjoy, please comment and seed.
